{"tid":1373870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防具搜到又如何？又唔係武器","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:28:57.000Z","uid":173326,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99943e17e1e3f1efffbd1fd50439e30343a5cb45","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>用完唔好亂掉，呢啲唔係武器，俾人搜到都唔怕。<br />\n如果俾人查身份證都驚就唔好學人講抗爭。</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警問點解帶防具出街，你就答：<br />\n而家警察落閘唔出勤，市民戴保護裝備出街好合理！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今晚727有兩個情況嚴重，希望平安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話防具好重要<br />\n[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"},{"pid":"0b416ad2584cfc616ce4455bb23994035d68e6d8","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5351bfe5d4aaa1a13d1c4eb1ffeb650e63f1cf42","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a454fd5d7ed333f6447da44d8158fee408e612","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要唔係武器就唔洗驚，好似救生衣咁，唔會有法例話唔俾</span>"},{"pid":"338307789190133166082a88944d8849025c9767","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88da53d31f9e8da6b0822631a156c6bfb07f94f3","tid":1373870,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"有攻擊性嘅先